1.Text: "Your ex calls you and wants to work things out. Shame she cheated on you with your best friend though."

2.Text: "Your hot water heater decided to give you the cold shoulder... literally, that shower was awful."

3.Text: "Hey you know that game series you like? Well, there's a new one on the way!"

4.Text: "Some Mormons came and knocked on your door for what felt like half an hour. Guess they can't take a hint."

5.Text: "You could've sworn your coffee table wasn't there before, but your swollen toe tells you otherwise."

6.Text: "Well looks like the heartless folks at Comcast gave you a free month of Hulu."

7.Text: "You won the lottery!!! Well, only 20 bucks, but you still won the lottery."

8.Text: "Something smelled funny for awhile, and once you found the dead rat you kinda figured out what."

9.Text: "Turns out you got charged for you and your neighbors power last month, so congrats on no power bill this month!"

10.Text: "You checked you email and found coupons for your favorite snacks, and free delivery on top of it!"

11.Text: "Your brother called to give you updates on your nieces. They grow up so fast."

12.Text: "Your boss called to check in on you while you quarantine, showing he cares. He proceeded to bitch about quotas not being met because of everyone getting quarantined, showing he doesn't care THAT much."

13.Text: "You got one of the "premium" channels for free, and spent a while enjoying it."

14.Text: "Should you have trusted a fart after a dinner of beans and rice? No. Did you trust it? Unfortunately."

15.Text: "Your old friend from middle school messaged you, and you enjoyed talking to him after all this time."

16.Text: "A friend sent you a funny meme, showing you they are thinking of you."

17.Text: "A game on your wishlist is finally on sale."

19.Text: "Out from left field comes a random bill you forgot about."

21.Text: "Email notification from a friend about unusual activity on your social media account."

23.Text: "Suddenly woke up after an unexpected nap, feeling great!"
